description: Absolute stunning, duplex-style PENTHOUSE, 2Bed 2.5Bath w/DEEDED GARAGE PARKING + PRIVATE ROOF DECK w/gas connection for grilling! This unit is an entertainer's dream and lives like a true home in South Boston's most desirable location. The main living area offers an open floor plan with an excellent layout. There is a large kitchen with 4-seat island that opens to a spacious dining area equipped with a stylish dry bar. The dining area seamlessly flows into the large, corner exposure living room. Find a 1/2 bath & laundry on this level, which also has oversized windows & towering ceilings offering amazing natural light. Head upstairs to find two large bedrooms, including a primary with an ensuite bath, a second full bath, and a versatile bonus room great for work from home use or a play / entertainment area. This is also where you access your private roof deck with sweeping views of the city. Professionally managed, Pet-Friendly, Elevator Building, 2017 Construction. EASY TO SHOW!
